          code: `def max_sum_subarray(nums, k):
    if len(nums) < k:
        return 0

    # Calculate initial window sum
    window_sum = sum(nums[:k])
    max_sum = window_sum

    # Slide the window
    for i in range(k, len(nums)):
        window_sum += nums[i] - nums[i - k]  # Add right, remove left
        max_sum = max(max_sum, window_sum)

    return max_sum`
